import React, { useContext, useEffect, useState } from 'react'; import styles from './styles/PartPage.module.css' import ButtonBuy from '../components/UI/button/ButtonBuy'; import { useParams } from 'react-router-dom'; import { fetchOneParts} from '../http/partAPI'; import CategoryBar from '../components/UI/categoryBar/CategoryBar'; import BrandBar from '../components/UI/brandBar/BrandBar'; const PartPage = () => { const [part, setPart] = useState({}) const {id} = useParams() let availability = 0 const AvailabilityPart = () => { availability = part.diksona + part.lado + part.semaf + part.kalinina return availability } AvailabilityPart() useEffect(() => { fetchOneParts(id).then(data => setPart(data)) }, []) return (

{part.name_parts}

Бренд: {part.brands}
Номер производителя: {part.number_brand}
Аналоги: {part.analogue}
Группа: {part.groups}
Артикул: {part.id}
Есть в наличии
{Intl.NumberFormat('ru-RU', { style: 'currency', currency: 'RUB' }).format(part.price)}
: Нет в наличии
); }; export default PartPage;
